content:
Hi, I choose Ruslan's Kingdom, basically for 3 reasons:

1-My friends are in it;
2-I had already played in the kingdom Ydvia on the pioneer server;
3-He is the most beautiful king of the 3 and still reminds us of "The Chronicles of Narnia".

Unfortunately, the initial prizes were only in the kingdom of Ydvia, even so, Ruslan was my choice and the choice of the BR community. We are looking forward to the arrival of servers in America and the translation of the game into Portuguese! strong hug!

Thanks!
